Before I knew him,
I couldn't even drive a car.

00:20:18.351 --> 00:20:21.221 position:19% line:83% align:start
Since the day we met,
my mind has been at ease.

00:20:22.657 --> 00:20:24.992 position:21% line:83% align:start
The inner confidence
the priest helped me find,

00:20:25.026 --> 00:20:26.794 position:5% line:89% align:start
