00:20:26.828 --> 00:20:29.931 position:19% line:83% align:start
Protecting the Father
is my reason for existing.

00:20:31.364 --> 00:20:33.601 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Rikiel] He is currently
going through a change.

00:20:33.634 --> 00:20:36.303 position:16% line:83% align:start
His beliefs and the will
of the man named Dio

00:20:36.336 --> 00:20:38.740 position:19% line:83% align:start
