to Father Pucchi's side.

00:20:43.711 --> 00:20:46.346 position:16% line:83% align:start
Everything we've done is
to guide the priest

00:20:46.379 --> 00:20:48.716 position:21% line:83% align:start
and raise him up to
his ultimate destiny

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:50.250 position:21% line:89% align:start
