00:21:12.006 --> 00:21:14.876 position:10% line:83% align:start
I see now it doesn't matter
who the victor is.

00:21:14.909 --> 00:21:17.011 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can't believe
I couldn't see it before.

00:21:18.112 --> 00:21:19.547 position:16% line:89% align:start
