is in search of.

00:21:22.517 --> 00:21:25.186 position:19% line:83% align:start
The happenstances that
aided you up to this moment.

00:21:25.219 --> 00:21:27.420 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Rikiel] That's what he wants.

00:21:27.454 --> 00:21:30.758 position:19% line:83% align:start
Clearly, you have fate
backing you up in your corner.

00:21:32.026 --> 00:21:33.393 position:35% line:89% align:start
Was it me?

00:21:33.426 --> 00:21:35.129 position:19% line:89% align:start
Or was it always you?

00:21:35.163 --> 00:21:36.697 position:16% line:83% align:start
